
'''''Nakom''''' ni filime yikinamico yakozwe mu mwaka wa 2016 iyobowe na Kelly Daniela Norris na TW Pittman <ref>Nakom :: Film Movement

\</ref>.  Iyi filime yagaragaye bwa mbere ku isi mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime rya 66 rya Berlin mu gice cya Panorama  kandi yatumiriwe kuzerekanwa bwa mbere muri [[Amerika]] y'Amajyaruguru mu iserukiramuco rya new diroctorss i New York<ref>Review: A Father Dies, and Duty Weighs on a Son in 'Nakom' <nowiki>https://www.nytimes.com</nowiki> › 2017/03/02 › movies › nak...</ref>. 

== Umugambi ==
''Nakom'' inkuru yimbitse yaturutse mu majyaruguru ya [[Gana]], Nakom akurikira Iddrisu, umunyeshuri w’ubuvuzi ufite ubuhanga ugomba gusubira mu mudugudu w'iwabo nyuma y'urupfu rutunguranye rwa se maze agaharanira ko umuryango we ubaho.<ref>Nakom by Kelly Norris and TW Pittman | Corinth Films <nowiki>http://corinthfilms.com</nowiki> › films › nakom</ref>

